s\u003E\n","\u003C/svg\u003E\n"],"text/plain":["\u003CFigure size 500x250 with 1 Axes\u003E"]},"metadata":{},"output_type":"display_data"}],"source":["# 清除以前的梯度\n","#x.grad：PyTorch 会把 x 的梯度（导数）存在 x.grad 这个属性里，第一次计算梯度前它是 None，但如果之前算过其他梯度（比如 ReLU 的梯度），x.grad 里会有旧值；\n","#.data：访问 x.grad 张量的 “原始数值部分”（新手可以暂时理解为 “必须加这一步才能清空”）；\n","#.zero_()：这是 PyTorch 的 “原地清零” 函数（函数名末尾的 _ 表示 “原地修改”，不创建新张量），把 x.grad 里的所有元素都变成 0。\n","x.grad.data.zero_()\n","# 让 PyTorch 自动算出 ReLU 输出 y 对输入 x 的导数（梯度），并把结果存在 x.grad 里。\n","y.backward(torch.ones_like(x),retain_graph=True)\n","d2l.plot(x.detach(), x.grad, 'x', 'grad of sigmoid', figsize=(5, 2.5))"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"f2c210b5","metadata":{},"source":"\u003Ch3\u003E\n\u003Ca id=\"tanh函数\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#tanh%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0\"\u003E\u003C/a\u003Etanh函数\u003C/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E与sigmoid函数类似，\n[\u003Cstrong\u003Etanh(双曲正切)函数也能将其输入压缩转换到区间(-1, 1)上\u003C/strong\u003E]。\ntanh函数的公式如下：\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E(\u003Cstrong\u003E$$\\operatorname{tanh}(x) = \\frac{1 - \\exp(-2x)}{1 + \\exp(-2x)}.$$\u003C/strong\u003E)\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E下面我们绘制tanh函数。\n注意，当输入在0附近时，tanh函数接近线性变换。\n函数的形状类似于sigmoid函数，\n不同的是tanh函数关于坐标系原点中心对称。\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003Etanh 函数（双曲正切函数）是深度学习中经典的激活函数，核心作用是把任意实数映射到 -1~1 之间，解决了 Sigmoid 函数 “输出非 0 均值” 的问题，\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EThe tanh Function(Hyperbolic Tangent)is a classic activation function in deep learning.Its core function is to moap any real number to the range between -1~1.Crucially,it solves the \"non-zero-centered output\"problem associated with the Sigmoid function.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003Etanh 能用来干啥？\n隐藏层激活函数：在 ReLU 普及前，tanh 是比 Sigmoid 更常用的隐藏层激活函数 —— 因为输出是 0 均值，反向传播时梯度更新更高效（不会像 Sigmoid 那样梯度全正 / 全负）；\n序列模型（如 RNN）：早期 RNN、LSTM 中常用来处理时序数据，平衡正负值的表达；\n注意：输出层很少用—— 输出层做二分类用 Sigmoid（0~1 表示概率），做多分类用 Softmax，tanh 一般只用于隐藏层。\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EActivation Function for Hidden Layers: Before ReLU became ubiquitous, tanh was more commonly used in hidden layers than Sigmoid. This is because its zero-centered output leads to more efficient gradient updates during backpropagation (avoiding the \"all positive/all negative\" gradient issue seen in Sigmoid).\nSequence Models (e.g., RNNs): It is frequently used in early RNNs and LSTMs for processing sequential data, as it effectively balances the representation of positive and negative values.\nNote: It is rarely used in output layers. For binary classification, Sigmoid is preferred (outputting 0~1 probabilities), and for multi-class classification, Softmax is used. Tanh is generally restricted to hidden layers.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003Etanh 函数核心是，能把任意实数映射到 -1 ~ 1 之间，且输出是 0 均值；\n主要用在深度学习隐藏层（尤其是早期序列模型），解决了 Sigmoid 非 0 均值的问题；\n最大缺点是仍存在梯度消失，计算成本也高于 ReLU，因此现在隐藏层主流还是用 ReLU。\u003C/p\u003E"},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":7,"id":"2e789b42","metadata":{},"outputs":[{"data":{"image/svg+xml":["\u003C?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"no\"?\u003E\n","\u003C!DOCTYPE svg PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD SVG 1.1//EN\"\n","  \"http://www.w3.org/Graphics/SVG/1.1/DTD/svg11.dtd\"\u003E\n","\u003Csvg xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" width=\"338.360937pt\" height=\"183.35625pt\" viewBox=\"0 0 338.360937 183.35625\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" version=\"1.1\"\u003E\n"," \u003Cmetadata\u003E\n","  \u003Crdf:RDF xmlns:dc=\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\" xmlns:cc=\"http://creativecommons.org/ns#\" xmlns:rdf=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#\"\u003E\n","   \u003Ccc:Work\u003E\n","    \u003Cdc:type rdf:resource=\"http://purl.org/dc/dcmitype/StillImage\"/\u003E\n","    \u003Cdc:date\u003E2026-03-19T04:29:02.838350\u003C/dc:date\u003E\n","    \u003Cdc:format\u003Eimage/svg+xml\u003C/dc:format\u003E\n","    \u003Cdc:creator\u003E\n","     \u003Ccc:Agent\u003E\n","      \u003Cdc:title\u003EMatplotlib v3.7.5, https://matplotlib.org/\u003C/dc:title\u003E\n","     \u003C/cc:Agent\u003E\n","    \u003C/dc:creator\u003E\n","   \u003C/cc:Work\u003E\n","  \u003C/rdf:RDF\u003E\n"," \u0